{
  "stem": "17526.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we were debating, shall we trade it for bread, shall we trade it for cigarettes, or shall we eat the chocolate as it is?",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We both decided we'd eat the chocolate as it is.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We were so starved.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "This camp, this particular camp, which was-- I spent most of the time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Every day after work coming back, you stayed on the [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The [GERMAN] is the plant.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And the work was hard-- labor, manual work.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we had to do so much.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we had kapos overseeing us, naturally, to see if we were doing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You couldn't goof.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I-- I had very good-- in this particular camp for a while, I-- I had-- I was a privileged character.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The foreman of this particular column, of this particular battalion, [BACKROUND NOISE] so to speak, took a liking to me, and he kept me as a shop steward.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was in the shop inside, issuing the tools, collecting different things, and seeing that everything is right.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he also favored me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I told him I'm an artist.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He asked me if I could draw a-- a portrait of his girlfriend.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said, sure.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Why not?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Anything to get some kind of favor of some kind.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So he gave me a picture of a beautiful German girl, and I carried around [INAUDIBLE] respectively thinking that it was impossible for me draw any pictures at all.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I didn't have the materials, I didn't have the space-- the place.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was just in it-- but anyway, one day I'm walking-- he sends me with an errand to another place.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I'm riding on a bicycle [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Within the plant, you were free to move.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Of course, we have to do some work.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
